title: Total Currency Outside the Treasury for United States
notes:
Series Is Presented Here As Two Variables--(1)--Original Data, 1878-1914 (2)--Original Data, 1914-1949. Data Exclude Minor Coin. First Of Month Data In The Source Are Presented Here As End Of Month Data. Source: U.S. Treasury Department, Computed By NBER From Data Found In Annual Report Of The Treasurer, 1886; And Circulation Statement Of U.S. Money Since 1887.

This NBER data series m14135a appears on the NBER website in Chapter 14 at http://www.nber.org/databases/macrohistory/contents/chapter14.html.
